-grossing tour behind [[Taylor Swift]] and One Direction (Pollstar Year End Top 100 Worldwide tours of 2015).\nThe tour grossed $180 million from 54 shows in 2015.<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.pollstarpro.com/files/charts2015/2015YearEndTop100WorldwideTours.pdf |title = Pollstar &#124; Welcome to the New Pollstar!}}</ref> and $40.1 million from 32 shows in 2016.<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.pollstarpro.com/files/charts2016/2016YearEndTop100WorldwideTours.pdf |title = Pollstar &#124; Welcome to the New Pollstar!}}</ref> Total gross: $221.1 million from 86 shows performed.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em|group=\"nb\"}}\n\n'''Footnotes'''\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n{{AC/DC}}\n\n[[Category:AC/DC concert tours]]\n[[Category:2015 concert tours]]\n[[Category:2016 concert tours]]\n[[Category:Axl Rose]]\n", "name_user": "JHunterJ", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up, replaced: 0 million \u2192 0\u00a0million (3)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rock_or_Bust_World_Tour"}
